content.c_description: Empower advocates for support systems to improve policies specific to women’s needs in and outside of the workplace, including maternity leave, child care, women’s health, and more. We hope to direct our advocacy through mentorship programs within Yext that empower and advance all women. We are also working to leverage Yext’s reputation and brand to establish and build community among Women in Tech in NYC.
content.yext/name: Life at Yext | Empower: Recruit, Inspire and Advance Women at Yext
